---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Kenny Raymond">

  <section class="pt-28 pb-20 md:pb-28 px-6 md:px-10">

    <!-- Portrait -->
    <div class="w-44 h-44 md:w-28 md:h-28 rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-8 md:mb-6">
      <img
        src="/b&w ken big.png"
        alt="Kenny Raymond portrait"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold mb-8 md:mb-6">
      About Me
    </h1>

    <!-- Bio -->
    <div class="text-base leading-relaxed text-white/90 space-y-5 max-w-2xl">
      <p>I'm a Staff Product Designer with 10+ years of experience shaping high-impact consumer and b2b products.</p>
      <p>My work is anchored in two principles that show up in everything I build: ruthless simplicity and earned trust.</p>
      <p>My teammates describe me as a PM-design hybrid, with strengths in product strategy, storytelling, and aligning teams around a compelling vision.</p>
      <p>I'm at my best in environments that prioritize momentum, where I can learn by quickly building and shipping, rather than getting lost in docs and endless reviews.</p>
      <p>While I bring a high bar for craft and product rigor to the team, I'm equally intentional about building genuine human connections with everyone I work with.</p>
      <p>That balance of rigor and connection has shaped my career and contributed to recognition along the way, including one of the three Design Excellence Awards given by the LinkedIn Design Org in 2024.</p>
    </div>

  </section>

</Layout>
